name: A touch of innocence
description:
A touch of innocence 
Deadlines with my Demons #5 
#Herbie7777777 
CN 
--------------
White noise on the TV. 
The point of no return has been passed. 
Shelter needs to be sought in order to stay sane since the real danger here is not directly life-threatening. 
It's scratching, crushing, meddling with mental structures that should best be left alone so they can flourish. 
There is a hand in my pants and a shard lodged in my brain. 
----
I am taking care of it by minting this artwork.
Thank you for your attention.
--------------
